rdpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/bg-recruit-message-768x296.jpg 768w, https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/bg-recruit-message-1536x592.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1640px) 100vw, 1640px\" /><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignfull are-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\"><div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"735\" height=\"385\" src=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/recruit-msg.png\" alt=\"従業員自らいろいろな事にチャレンジ\" class=\"wp-image-1005\" srcset=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/recruit-msg.png 735w, https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/recruit-msg-390x204.png 390w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px\" /></figure></div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center has-background is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(18deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.74) 0%,rgba(255,255,255,0.92) 100%);flex-basis:50%\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group text-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">求職者のみなさんへ、人生の先輩としてアドバイスします。</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">頭だけで考えるのではなく、まずは会社見学に行ってみましょう。<br>「現地現物」自分の目で、しっかりと視てみましょう。</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">自分の人生を応援してくれる企業にきっと会えます。<br>(株)北日本朝日航洋は、岩手と共に、成長したい貴方を応援します！</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">人生を共に歩いていきましょう。</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">当社では、目標を掲げて頑張る人財を様々な制度で支援すると共に、お互いが切磋琢磨しながら成長できる環境があります。</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-sheer\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/recruit/seek\">求める人材へ</a></div>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull recruit-ttl recruit-ttl-interview\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#005dab\">INTERVIEW</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"> 先輩社員の一日 </h2>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<p>若手社員たちが自分の仕事に対して、どのような思いで取り組んでいるか、それぞれの社員の声をお聞きください。</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"recruit-interview-links\"><li><a href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/recruit/oneday/oneday1\" class=\"recruit-page-link\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"360\" height=\"460\" src=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/senpai01.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/senpai01.jpg 360w, https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/senpai01-305x390.jpg 305w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /><p class=\"shain-shokusyu shokusyu1\">営業職</p><p class=\"shain-nyusya\">2014年新卒入社</p><p class=\"shain-busyo\">営業部　営業推進グループ</p></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/recruit/oneday/oneday5\" class=\"recruit-page-link\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"360\" height=\"460\" src=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/a11b4bb3ba448d1fa402ac3dc62cc91f-1.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/a11b4bb3ba448d1fa402ac3dc62cc91f-1.jpg 360w, https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/a11b4bb3ba448d1fa402ac3dc62cc91f-1-305x390.jpg 305w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /><p class=\"shain-shokusyu shokusyu3\">技術職</p><p class=\"shain-nyusya\">2015年新卒入社</p><p class=\"shain-busyo\">空間情報コンサルタント部　コンサルタントグループ</p></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/recruit/oneday/oneday4\" class=\"recruit-page-link\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"360\" height=\"460\" src=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/thumbnail.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/thumbnail.jpg 360w, https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/thumbnail-305x390.jpg 305w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /><p class=\"shain-shokusyu shokusyu3\">技術職</p><p class=\"shain-nyusya\">2020年新卒入社</p><p class=\"shain-busyo\">空間情報コンサルタント部　地理情報グループ</p></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/recruit/oneday/oneday7\" class=\"recruit-page-link\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"360\" height=\"460\" src=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/a11b4bb3ba448d1fa402ac3dc62cc91f.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/a11b4bb3ba448d1fa402ac3dc62cc91f.jpg 360w, https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/a11b4bb3ba448d1fa402ac3dc62cc91f-305x390.jpg 305w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /><p class=\"shain-shokusyu shokusyu3\">技術職</p><p class=\"shain-nyusya\">2022年新卒入社</p><p class=\"shain-busyo\">空間情報コンサルタント部　資産情報グループ</p></a></li></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-horizontal is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-499968f5 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-sheer\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/recruit/oneday\">先輩社員の一日へ</a></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns recruit-bnrs is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:735px\"><div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/recruit/welfare\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"735\" height=\"260\" src=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/recruit-bnr-welfare.png\" alt=\"福利厚生\" class=\"wp-image-1007\" srcset=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/recruit-bnr-welfare.png 735w, https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/recruit-bnr-welfare-390x138.png 390w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px\" /></a></figure></div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:735px\"><div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/recruit/requirements\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"735\" height=\"260\" src=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/recruit-bnr-recruitment.png\" alt=\"募集要項\" class=\"wp-image-1006\" srcset=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/recruit-bnr-recruitment.png 735w, https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/recruit-bnr-recruitment-390x138.png 390w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px\" /></a></figure></div></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull recruit-link\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-100 has-background-dim\" style=\"background-color:#005dab\"></span><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull recruit-ttl recruit-ttl-link\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<p>LINK</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">リンク</h2>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"is-style-external-link\"><a href=\"https://ginga.or.jp/kirari/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">いわてキラリ企業就職ナビサイト</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"is-style-external-link\"><a href=\"https://www.furusato-i.or.jp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ふるさといわて定住財団</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"is-style-external-link\"><a href=\"https://www.shigotoba-iwate.com/kyujin/detail/030007-000026/pr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">いわてで働こう推進協議会｜シゴトバ クラシバ いわて</a></p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull recruit-ttl recruit-ttl-entry\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#005dab\">ENTRY / CONTACT</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">エントリー / お問い合わせ</h2>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<p>採用試験エントリーやお問い合わせは、お問い合わせメールフォームとお電話から受け付けています。<br>新卒採用の会社見学会の開催日についてはホームページ上でお知らせいたします。</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns recruit-entry-bnrs is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:695px\"><div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/contact\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"695\" height=\"138\" src=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/recruit-bnr-contact.png\" alt=\"お問い合わせ\" class=\"wp-image-1010\" srcset=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/recruit-bnr-contact.png 695w, https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/recruit-bnr-contact-390x77.png 390w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 695px) 100vw, 695px\" /></a></figure></div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:725px\"><div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"725\" height=\"138\" src=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/recruit-bnr-tel.png\" alt=\"019-651-5311 受付時間9:00～17:00\" class=\"wp-image-1504\" srcset=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/recruit-bnr-tel.png 725w, https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/recruit-bnr-tel-390x74.png 390w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 725px) 100vw, 725px\" /></figure></div></div>\n</div>\n\r\n\t\t</main>\r\n\r\n\t</div>\r\n\r\n\t<footer class=\"site-footer\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"footer-inner\">\r\n\t\t\t<ul class=\"footer-nav\"><li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-home menu-item-1020\"><a href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/\">北日本朝日航洋公式サイト</a></li>\n<li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-1021\"><a href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/company\">企業情報</a></li>\n<li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-1023\"><a href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/company/securitypolicy\">情報セキュリティポリシー</a></li>\n<li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-1022\"><a href=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/company/privacypolicy\">個人情報保護方針</a></li>\n</ul>\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"footer-address\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"logos\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://privacymark.jp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nj-aac/img/logo-privacy.jpg?2\" alt=\"プライバシーマーク\"></a>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.mhlw.go.jp/stf/seisakunitsuite/bunya/kodomo/shokuba_kosodate/kurumin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nj-aac/img/logo-kurumin2022.jpg\" alt=\"くるみんマーク\"></a>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<a><img src=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nj-aac/img/logo-health-and-productivity-2024.jpg\" alt=\"健康経営優良法人2024\"></a>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<a><img src=\"https://www.nj-aac.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nj-aac/img/logo-ikusei-r6.jpg\" alt=\"いわて産業人材奨学金返還支援制度\"></a>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<p>北日本朝日航洋は、プライバシーマーク、くるみんマーク、健康経営優良法人、いわて産業人材奨学金返還支援制度の認定を取得しています。</p>\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<small class=\"copyright\">&copy;2010-2021 North Japan Aero Asahi Corporation</small>\r\n\t</footer>\r\n\r\n\t<script type=\"speculationrules\">\n{\"prefetch\":[{\"source\":\"document\",\"where\":{\"and\":[{\"href_matches\":\"\\/*\"},{\"not\":{\"href_matches\":[\"\\/wordpress\\/wp-*.php\",\"\\/wordpress\\/wp-admin\\/*\",\"\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/*\",\"\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/*\",\"\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/plugins\\/*\",\"\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/nj-aac\\/*\",\"\\/*\\\\?(.+)\"]}},{\"not\":{\"selector_matches\":\"a[rel~=\\\"nofollow\\\"]\"}},{\"not\":{\"selector_matches\":\".no-prefetch, .no-prefetch a\"}}]},\"eagerness\":\"conservative\"}]}\n</script>\n\t\t<style>\n\t\t\t:root {\n\t\t\t\t-webkit-user-select: none;\n\t\t\t\t-webkit-touch-callout: none;\n\t\t\t\t-ms-user-select: none;\n\t\t\t\t-moz-user-select: none;\n\t\t\t\tuser-select: none;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n\t\t\t/*<![CDATA[*/\n\t\t\tdocument.oncontextmenu = function(event) {\n\t\t\t\tif (event.target.tagName != 'INPUT' && event.target.tagName != 'TEXTAREA') {\n\t\t\t\t\tevent.preventDefault();\n\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t};\n\t\t\tdocument.ondragstart = function() {\n\t\t\t\tif (event.target.tagName != 'INPUT' && event.target.tagName != 'TEXTAREA') {\n\t\t\t\t\tevent.preventDefault();\n\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t};\n\t\t\t/*]]>*/\n\t\t</script>\n\t\t<style id='core-block-supports-inline-css' type='text/css'>\n.wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7{flex-wrap:nowrap;}.wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-499968f5{justify-content:center;}\n</style>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" id=\"vk-ltc-js-js-extra\">\n/* <![CDATA[ */\nvar vkLtc = {\"ajaxurl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.nj-aac.com\\/wordpress\\/wp-admin\\/admin-ajax.php\",\"editLabel\":\"